<event name="FREE_CRYSTAL" unique="true">
	<text load="TEXT_FREE_CRYSTAL"/>
	<weapon name="GIFTLIST_CRYSTAL"/>
	<choice>
		<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
		<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
	<choice>
		<text>Do nothing.</text>
		<event/>
	</choice>
</event>
<textList name="TEXT_FREE_CRYSTAL">
	<text>You notice the barebones wreckage of a nearby Crystalline vessel; though little scrap matter remains, it appears the scavengers overlooked a single Crystal weapon!</text>
	<text>A small Crystalline trader with a squeaky high-pitched voice hails you. "Foreigners! It is important we make peace with barbaric aliens, perhaps this free weapon of war will soothe you?"</text>
	<text>A Crystalline trading outpost hails you, requesting a trade. You look through your supply count until you realise their offer is a sample of foreign rocks in return for a military grade weapon... an offer you take in a hearbeat.</text>
</textList>

<event name="CRYSTAL_FOREIGNER_MAP" unique="true">
	<text>You notice another foreigner nearby, a ship of scout classification. They hail you and make a brief offer to sell you the map data they have been collecting from this sector.</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_FOREIGNER_SCOUT" hostile="false"/>
	<choice>
		<text>Buy the map data.</text>
		<event load="CRYSTAL_FOREIGNER_MAP_BUY"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>We can't verify the quality of their maps. Decline.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You decline the scout's offer and carry on.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<eventList name="CRYSTAL_FOREIGNER_MAP_BUY">   
	<event> 
		<text>The ship transfers over the map data to your ship's computer.</text>
		<reveal_map/>
		<item_modify>
			<item type="scrap" min="-20" max="-20"/>
		</item_modify>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>The ship transfers over the map data to your ship's computer.</text>
		<item_modify>
			<item type="scrap" min="-20" max="-20"/>
