		<text>Help them.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You board the ship, but it's already too late. A dying Zoltan in the corner manages to cough out some final words to you. "The Crystals- they were here... take this to them... You know what to do with it." The Zoltan slides over a package containing a large Zoltan-made bomb, and a letter noting some coordinates, then dissipates into nothing.</text>
