<eventList name="CRYSTALHOME_ZOLTENVOY_DELIVERY_GIFT">
	<event>
		<text>You hail the outpost and deliver the bomb. The Crystals inside are deeply confused, but not long after Zoltan reinforcements jump in! It seems you've misunderstood - the Zoltan were here to attack the Crystals! The peace-keeper vessel approaching seems to think you're working against them and attacks!</text>
