		<text>You hail the outpost and deliver the bomb. It appears you understood correctly, because the Crystals thank you. Whatever attacked the Zoltan must have been a pirate, probably using the Crystal weapons so commonly found around here. As thanks for finishing the delivery, the Crystals pay you handsomely.</text>
