<eventList name="CRYSTALHOME_ZOLTENVOY_DELIVERY_EXPLODE">
	<event>
		<text>You sneak into the outpost and place the bomb where it looks like it'll cause the most damage, then detonate it from a distance. It has a disastrous effect, and the Crystals are obviously not pleased. You hear them shouting, "Damn it, pirates must have taken out the envoy, and now they're attacking us too! Prepare for battle!" It seems you've misunderstood the Zoltan's intentions.</text>
